I went on RS2 Server Tutorials and seen a TuT say somethen about declaring, so i'm just talking to myself say "WTF is declaring?" (lol) and was just wondering what it was. I went and looked it up in a dictionary but that didnt succeed in knowing what declare means in Java, so I just need to know what declaring mean. Does anyone know what declaring mean? (Of course someone should know (lol).)
